      "(三)"
    ],
    "pages": [
      5
    ],
    "page_start": 5,
    "page_end": 5,
    "content": "(三)第一類期貨商資通系統應定期辦理系統滲透測試。",
    "is_leaf": true,
    "table_count": 0,
    "tables": []
  },
  {
    "file_name": "「網路安全防護自律規範」完整條文.md",
    "node_name": "(四)",
    "level": 2,
    "sibling_order": 4,
    "path_key": "6.3.4",
